'''格拉咸·羅拔·亞歷山大'''（{{lang-en|'''Graham Robert Alexander'''}}，{{bd|1971年|10月10日|catidx=Alexander, Graham}}）出生於[[英格蘭|英格蘭]][[考文垂|考文垂]]，是一名[[英式足球|足球]][[運動員|運動員]]，為[[蘇格蘭足球代表隊|蘇格蘭國腳]]，司職[[後衛_(足球)|右閘]]，但於球員黃昏期改踢[[中場|防守中場]]<ref name=autogenerated2>{{Cite web |url=http://www.burnleyfootballclub.premiumtv.co.uk/page/LatestHeadlines/0,,10413~1102381,00.html |title=Alexander The Seventh! {{!}} Burnley {{!}} News {{!}} Latest Headlines {{!}} Latest Headlines<!-- Bot generated title --> |accessdate=2009-11-03 |archive-date=2019-08-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190824023635/http://www.burnleyfootballclub.premiumtv.co.uk/page/LatestHeadlines/0,,10413~1102381,00.html |dead-url=yes }}</ref>，他早年在[[斯坎索普联足球俱乐部|斯肯索普]]亦曾擔任這個位置<ref name=autogenerated4>{{Cite web |url=http://www.scottishfa.co.uk/player_details.cfm?playerid=35468&squadid=1 |title=Scottish Football Association: The Scottish FA: Scotland :<!-- Bot generated title --> |access-date=2009-11-03 |archive-date=2008-12-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081212050036/http://www.scottishfa.co.uk/player_details.cfm?playerid=35468&squadid=1 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，而他現時是[[英超|英超]]第三名最年長的入球球員<ref>{{cite web |language=en |url=http://www.statbunker.com/football/ktg/index.php?PL=ktgalltime&Code=EPL&statType=oldest_gs |title=English Premier League / All Time / Oldest Goal Scorers |publisher=statbunker.com |date=2009-11-03 |accessdate=2009-12-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091020222131/http://www.statbunker.com/football/ktg/index.php?PL=ktgalltime&Code=EPL&statType=oldest_gs |archive-date=2009-10-20 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>，並在職業球員生涯上陣超越1,000場<ref name="1,000 club">{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/blogs/paulfletcher/2011/04/alexander_joins_the_1000_club.html#286904 |title=Alexander the great joins the 1,000 club |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2011-04-17 |accessdate=2011-04-19 |archive-date=2019-09-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190911175458/https://www.bbc.co.uk/blogs/paulfletcher/2011/04/alexander_joins_the_1000_club.html#286904 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2012年6月退役後留在[[英甲|英甲]]球會[[普雷斯顿足球俱乐部|普雷斯頓]]擔任青訓主管。於2012年12月出任[[英乙|英乙]]球會[[弗利特伍德镇足球俱乐部|費列活特]]的領隊，並帶領球隊透過附加賽升班[[英甲|英甲]]。現時任教[[英格蘭足球全國聯賽|英格蘭足球全國聯賽]]球會[[沙福特城足球會|沙福特城]]。

==生平==
===球員===
====球會====
;斯肯索普及盧頓
亞歷山大於1980年代末期在[[斯坎索普联足球俱乐部|斯肯索普]]青年軍展開足球事業，他於1991年4月27日首次代表一隊上陣，以後補身份入替馬克·軒尼（Mark Hine），同年並且與球隊簽下首張職業球員合約。1991/92年球季亞歷山大已在斯肯索普一隊陣中成為固定成員，通常擔任[[後衛_(足球)|右閘]]位置。在以10萬[[英鎊|英鎊]]轉投[[卢顿足球俱乐部|盧頓]]前，他為斯肯索普上陣超過200場<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/p/preston/2151067.stm |title=Alexander eyes Iron tie |work=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2002-07-25 |accessdate=2009-11-03 |archive-date=2019-08-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190823020909/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/p/preston/2151067.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.soccerbase.com/players_details.sd?playerid=87 |title=www.soccerbase.com - The Internet Soccer Database<!-- Bot generated title --> |access-date=2009-11-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081005051355/http://www.soccerbase.com/players_details.sd?playerid=87 |archive-date=2008-10-05 |dead-url=yes }}</ref></small>，在他為盧頓效力的4年內，亦為球隊上陣相近的場數。 

;普雷斯頓
1999年[[伯恩利足球俱乐部|般尼]]與[[普雷斯顿足球俱乐部|普雷斯頓]]分別爭取亞歷山大加盟，最終他選擇投效普雷斯頓<small><ref>[http://www.clarets-mad.co.uk/news/loadnews.asp?cid=TMNW&id=350838 Graham Alexander is finally a Claret - Burnley FC - Clarets MAD<!-- Bot generated title -->] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070927175400/http://www.clarets-mad.co.uk/news/loadnews.asp?cid=TMNW&id=350838 |date=2007-09-27 }}</ref></small>，隨即成為[[迪普戴爾球場|迪普戴爾球場]]（Deepdale）中一隊的常規正選，其後更獲委擔任[[隊長_(足球)|隊長]]，亦是球隊主踢[[自由球|罰球]]的球員，同時擔任[[十二碼|十二碼]]的劊子手<small><ref name=autogenerated3>[http://www.burnleyfootballclub.premiumtv.co.uk/page/ProfilesDetail/0,,10413~8811,00.html Graham Alexander | Burnley | Team | Profiles<!-- Bot generated title -->] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080517023444/http://www.burnleyfootballclub.premiumtv.co.uk/page/ProfilesDetail/0,,10413~8811,00.html |date=2008-05-17 }}</ref></small>。在亞歷山大的球員生涯中一直保持健康，沒有遭受嚴重傷患，直到2000/01年球季在作客[[伍尔弗汉普顿流浪足球俱乐部|狼隊]]時撞斷[[肋骨|肋骨]]才缺陣數星期<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/p/preston/1090991.stm |title=Alexander injury blow for Preston |work=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2000-12-28 |accessdate=2009-11-03 |archive-date=2016-03-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160308193101/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/p/preston/1090991.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。2004年3月10日亞歷山大續約兩年<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/p/preston/3498718.stm |title=Alexander signs new deal |work=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2004-03-10 |accessdate=2009-11-03 |archive-date=2019-08-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190822232726/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/p/preston/3498718.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。在普雷斯頓效力8個年頭，亞歷山大剛好為球隊上陣400場，於2007年8月25日對[[科尔切斯特联足球俱乐部|高車士打]]是他為球隊第400場及最後一場上陣<small><ref>[http://www.pnefc.premiumtv.co.uk/page/NewsDetail/0,,10362~1098579,00.html 400 Up For Grezza | Preston North End | News | Latest | Latest<!-- Bot generated title -->] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070826141331/http://www.pnefc.premiumtv.co.uk/page/NewsDetail/0,,10362~1098579,00.html |date=2007-08-26 }}</ref></small>。亞歷山大入選2004/05年度[[英格蘭職業足球運動員協會|PFA]][[英格蘭足球冠軍聯賽|英冠]][[PFA年度最佳陣容|年度最佳陣容]]<small><ref name=autogenerated3 /></small>。 

在2006年夏季亞歷山大已與數支球隊扯上關係，其中包括出價5萬[[英鎊|英鎊]]被拒的[[水晶宫足球俱乐部|水晶宮]]，普雷斯頓並稱：
<blockquote>
『他是球隊隊長及陣中重要一員，絕非我們准許離隊的球員。』<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/p/preston/5221206.stm |title=Preston reject bid for Alexander |work=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2006-07-27 |accessdate=2009-11-03 |archive-date=2019-08-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190824203925/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/p/preston/5221206.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>
</blockquote>

2007年8月29日亞歷山大使人驚訝地轉投[[兰开夏郡|兰开夏郡]]敵對球會[[伯恩利足球俱乐部|般尼]]，導致他離隊的主要原因是普雷斯頓未能延長其尚餘一年的合約<small><ref>[http://www.pnefc.premiumtv.co.uk/page/NewsDetail/0,,10362~1103387,00.html Grezza's Emotional Farewell | Preston North End | News | Latest | Latest<!-- Bot generated title -->]{{dead link|date=2018年3月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref></small>，相反般尼願意提供一張兩年期的合約，亞歷山大因而以20萬[[英鎊|英鎊]]轉戰[[摩亞球場|摩亞球場]]（Turf Moor）<small><ref name=autogenerated5>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/p/preston/6970677.stm |title=Burnley recruit PNE's Alexander |work=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2007-08-31 |accessdate=2009-11-03 |archive-date=2019-08-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190820091139/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/p/preston/6970677.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。普雷斯頓的主席德雷克·肖（Derek Shaw）不願失去亞歷山大並說：

 <blockquote>
『我們並不特別希望賣走格拉咸，但他到般尼可以獲得兩年合約，而留在迪普戴爾卻只有一年。他是一名健康的球員，我們是極有可能延長格拉咸的合約。』<small><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.lep.co.uk/WebPartsTpls/sport?articleid=3161836 |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2007-08-31 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070928014308/http://www.lep.co.uk/WebPartsTpls/sport?articleid=3161836 |archivedate=2007-09-28 }}</ref><ref name=autogenerated5 /></small>
</blockquote>

在亞歷山大離隊後普雷斯頓的領隊[[Paul_Simpson_(footballer)|保罗·辛普森]]（Paul Simpson）亦有類似的評論，但堅持不會為一名年已35歲的球員提供兩年合約。亞歷山大的20萬鎊轉會費分兩期支付，首期10萬鎊即付，餘下10萬鎊於2008年夏季清付<small><ref name=autogenerated2 /></small>。

;般尼
2008/09年球季亞歷山大在般尼整季的61場聯賽及盃賽悉數正選上陣，射入11球，轉任防守中場角色，僅被罰一面[[黃牌|黃牌]]，更獲領隊[[欧文·科尔|欧文·科尔]]（Owen Coyle）的高度讚揚<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/b/burnley/7621155.stm |title=Coyle praises veteran Alexander |work=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2008-09-17 |accessdate=2009-11-03 |archive-date=2019-08-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190824034137/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/b/burnley/7621155.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，協助球隊透過附加賽升班[[英超|英超]]，是他個人7度參加附加賽以來首次獲得升班資格<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/8060970.stm |title=Burnley 1-0 Sheff Utd |work=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2009-05-25 |accessdate=2009-11-03 |archive-date=2012-08-16 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/69xakmMHg?url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/8060970.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，2009年6月29日亞歷山大與球隊續簽一年新約，留隊到2010年<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/b/burnley/8123860.stm |title=Alexander pens new Burnley deal |work=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2009-06-29 |accessdate=2009-11-03 |archive-date=2019-08-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190823020912/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/b/burnley/8123860.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，同年8月15日亞歷山大成為歷來最年長首次亮相英超的球員。9月19日亞歷山大在主場對[[桑德兰足球俱乐部|新特蘭]]時射入[[十二碼|十二碼]]，是他個人首個英超入球，亦使他以37歲另344日成為英超歷來第7位最年長的入球球員；10月31日主場2-0擊敗[[赫尔城足球俱乐部|侯城]]，亞歷山大更包辦兩球<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/8333572.stm |title=Burnley 2-0 Hull |work=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2009-10-31 |accessdate=2009-11-03 |archive-date=2019-08-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190822232728/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/8333572.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，使他以38歲另21日超越[[加里·斯皮德|加里·斯皮德]]成為第6位最年長的入球球員。12月16日主場對[[阿森纳足球俱乐部|阿仙奴]]再射入一球[[十二碼|十二碼]]為球隊扳平1-1<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/8412225.stm |title=Burnley 1-1 Arsenal |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2009-12-16 |accessdate=2009-12-17 |archive-date=2020-12-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201221192857/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/8412225.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，生涯聯賽入球達到100大關，更以38歲另67日超越[[米克·夏福特|米克·夏福特]]（Mick Harford）成為第5位最年長的入球球員。在聯賽經歷三個多月入球荒後，他於4月10日作客[[赫尔城足球俱乐部|侯城]]連續射入兩球十二碼，協助球隊反勝4-1<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/8607332.stm |title=Hull 1-4 Burnley |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2010-04-10 |accessdate=2010-04-12 |archive-date=2010-04-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100412081000/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/8607332.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，取得本季首場客勝及保留一線護級希望，更跨越[[图加伊·克里莫格卢|-{zh-hans:图加伊; zh-hk:杜基;}-]]（Tugay Kerimoğlu）及[[马克·休斯|-{zh-hans:马克·休斯; zh-hk:馬克·曉士;}-]]，以38歲另182日進佔[[英超|英超]]最年長的入球球員第三位。雖然般尼最終降班收場，但作為球隊重心之一的亞歷山大仍獲球隊續約兩年<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11661_6147564,00.html |title=Burnley duo pen new deals |publisher=Sky Sports |date=2010-05-11 |accessdate=2010-05-11 |archive-date=2010-05-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100514145645/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11661_6147564,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。

2011年4月16日主場2-1擊敗[[斯旺西城足球俱乐部|-{zh-hans:斯旺西; zh-hk:史雲斯;}-]]，亞歷山大於完場前87分鐘後補上陣<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/13022994.stm |title=Burnley 2-1 Swansea |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2011-04-16 |accessdate=2011-04-19 |archive-date=2011-04-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110423065750/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/13022994.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，是他職業生涯第1,000場上陣，繼[[東尼·福特|東尼·福特]]（Tony Ford）後第二位非門將球員達到這個里程碑<ref name="1,000 club"/>。般尼將4月25日定為「格拉汉姆·亚历山大日」（''Graham Alexander Day''），於對[[朴茨茅斯足球俱乐部|樸茨茅夫]]賽前頒發紀念獎，同日的場刊「''Claret and You''」有25頁特集，而球會商店亦出售相關紀念品<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.burnleyfootballclub.com/page/LatestHeadlines/0,,10413~2343729,00.html |title=Graham Alexander Day |publisher=[[伯恩利足球俱乐部|''burnleyfootballclub.com'']] |date=2011-04-21 |accessdate=2011-04-22 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110424125616/http://www.burnleyfootballclub.com/page/LatestHeadlines/0,,10413~2343729,00.html |archivedate=2011年4月24日 |df= }}</ref>。7月4日亞歷山大與般尼提前一年解除合約離隊<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/14021460.stm |title=Burnley captain Graham Alexander leaves Clarets |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2011-07-04 |accessdate=2011-08-04 |archive-date=2011-07-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110715054210/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/14021460.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

;重返普雷斯頓
2011年8月3日亞歷山大加盟剛降班[[英甲|英甲]]的[[普雷斯顿足球俱乐部|普雷斯頓]]，簽約1年<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/14392301.stm |title=Graham Alexander re-joins Preston North End |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2011-08-03 |accessdate=2011-08-04 |archive-date=2011-08-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110807161338/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/14392301.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2011年9月24日主場對[[特兰米尔流浪者足球俱乐部|燦美爾]]，亞歷山大射入一記招牌[[十二碼|十二碼]]，為球隊先拔頭籌兼取得回歸後首球<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/14958277.stm |title=Preston 2-1 Tranmere |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2011-09-24 |accessdate=2011-10-11 |archive-date=2011-10-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111023094736/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/14958277.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。10月15日亞歷山大成為普雷斯頓歷來第二位年滿40歲的上陣球員<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/15243376.stm |title=Age is just a number - Graham Alexander |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2011-10-11 |accessdate=2011-10-10 |archive-date=2011-11-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111106124036/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/15243376.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

====國家隊====
亞歷山大雖然在[[英格蘭|英格蘭]]出生，但由於其父親是[[蘇格蘭人|蘇格蘭人]]而有資格代表[[蘇格蘭足球代表隊|蘇格蘭國家隊]]<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport3/worldcup2002/hi/team_pages/nigeria/newsid_1919000/1919326.stm |title=Vogts names squad for friendly |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2002-04-09 |accessdate=2009-11-03 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307210518/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport3/worldcup2002/hi/team_pages/nigeria/newsid_1919000/1919326.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，亞歷山大於2002年年已30歲才獲時任蘇格蘭領隊[[贝尔蒂·福格茨|福士]]徵召<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/scotland/1931823.stm |title=New boys raring to go |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2002-04-15 |accessdate=2009-11-03 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307030348/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/scotland/1931823.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，普雷斯頓會長兼前[[英格蘭足球代表隊|英格蘭]]名宿[[湯·芬尼|湯·芬尼]]表示看好他在蘇格蘭的前途<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/scotland/1922291.stm |title=Finney backs Alexander to shine |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2002-04-10 |accessdate=2009-11-03 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307023656/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/scotland/1922291.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，亞歷山大曾表示代表蘇格蘭是其踢足球主要追求的目標<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/1908913.stm |title=Alexander hoping for Scotland call |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2002-04-03 |accessdate=2009-11-03 |archive-date=2016-03-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160308190412/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/1908913.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。這個目標於4月17日終於達成，亞歷山大首次代表蘇格蘭於[[皮托德里球場|皮托德里球場]]（Pittodrie Stadium）[[友誼賽|友賽]]1-2負於[[尼日利亞國家足球隊|尼日利亞]]上陣<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport3/worldcup2002/hi/team_pages/nigeria/newsid_1918000/1918507.stm |title=Nigeria edge out Scots |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2002-04-17 |accessdate=2009-11-03 |archive-date=2020-11-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201116082444/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport3/worldcup2002/hi/team_pages/nigeria/newsid_1918000/1918507.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>；同年5月亞歷山大隨同國家隊訪問[[遠東|遠東]]，包括在[[香港|香港]]參加[[香港回歸盃足球賽|回歸盃]]<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport3/worldcup2002/hi/team_pages/south_africa/newsid_1996000/1996842.stm |title=S Africa struggle past Scots |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2002-05-20 |accessdate=2009-11-03 |archive-date=2012-10-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121020142323/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport3/worldcup2002/hi/team_pages/south_africa/newsid_1996000/1996842.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/scotland/2002159.stm |title=Scots stroll to victory |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2002-05-23 |accessdate=2009-11-03 |archive-date=2019-08-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190823102406/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/scotland/2002159.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>；他第25次代表蘇格蘭以1-0擊敗[[法國國家足球隊|法國]]；他亦是2006年贏得每年一度[[日本|日本]][[麒麟盃|麒麟盃]]的成員之一，蘇格蘭以5-1擊敗[[保加利亞國家足球隊|保加利亞]]，最後以0-0賽和主隊[[日本國家足球隊|日本]]奪標<small><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.rsssf.com/tablesk/kirin.html |title=Kirin Cup<!-- Bot generated title --> |access-date=2009-11-03 |archive-date=2007-08-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070821100635/http://www.rsssf.com/tablesk/kirin.html |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。

===教練及領隊===
;普雷斯頓
亞歷山大重返[[普雷斯顿足球俱乐部|普雷斯頓]]後於[[普雷斯頓2011年至2012年球季|2011/12年球季]]下半季開始協助教練團隊，在領隊[[菲爾·布朗|菲爾·布朗]]（Phil Brown）於2011年12月14日被撤職後與[[大衛·安斯禾夫|大衛·安斯禾夫]]（David Unsworth）共同擔任看守領隊<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/16178900 |title=Manager Phil Brown is sacked by Preston North End |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2011-12-14 |accessdate=2012-12-28 |archive-date=2013-12-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131230015151/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/16178900 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，直到翌年1月中新帥[[格拉咸·韋斯利|格拉咸·韋斯利]]（Graham Westley）上任才結束。亞歷山大以40歲高齡於球季結束後退役並獲委任為青訓發展主管<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/18525245 |title=Preston appoint Graham Alexander as head of youth development |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2012-06-20 |accessdate=2012-12-28 |archive-date=2012-06-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120623064912/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/18525245 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2012年12月6日亞歷山大獲[[英乙|英乙]]球會[[弗利特伍德镇足球俱乐部|費列活特]]聘請出任領隊<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/20627115 |title=Fleetwood Town appoint Graham Alexander as boss |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2012-12-06 |accessdate=2012-12-28 |archive-date=2016-01-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160113125154/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/20627115 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

